        "*Intro*\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "> If, like me, you grew up humming along to the Bare Necessities or, later in life, convincing yourself you could do justice to New York, New York in the shower, then this project may feel personally connected. Though as it turns out, teaching a machine to recognise what you are humming or whistling (even if you have been doing it your whole life, by the way, still constitutes you an amateur) is a harder problem than it sounds...\n",
        "\n",
