        "## 6.1 Overview\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "The experiments are structured as follows:\n",
        "\n",
        "1. All 5 models evaluated across all 3 dataset splits using default hyperparameters\n",
        "2. Hyperparameter tuning for kNN `(k)`, Random Forest `(max_depth)` and SVM `(C)`\n",
        "3. MFCC coefficient tuning `(n_mfcc: 13, 20, 40)`\n",
        "4. Ensemble experiments\n",
        "5. Ablation study\n",
        "6. Confusion matrix result analysis\n",
        "\n",
        "All results are interpreted against the random chance baseline of 12.5% (1/8 classes).\n",
        "\n",
        "Note that Section 4.1 describes the final optimised pipeline. Section 6 henceforth documents the iterative process by which that pipeline was developed, starting from `n_mfcc=13` and the 29-feature vector, before tuning the number of MFCC coefficients later in Section 6.3, which ultimately confirms the final 29-feature vector used in all subsequent experiments.\n",
        "\n",
        "All models in Section 6.2 therefore use `n_mfcc=13` and a 29-feature vector as a starting point. Hyperparameter tuning for kNN, Random Forest and SVM takes place within their respective model sections below.\n",
